OL,3,CRapist police officer jailed
OL,5,FA police officer who raped a woman
OL,6,Fwhile off-duty has been jailed.
OL,8,FPC Benjamin Bottomley, 23, from
OL,9,FKirklees, was found guilty of rape and
OL,10,Fsexual assault after a trial at
OL,11,FSheffield Crown Court.
OL,13,FHe attacked the victim, an adult
OL,14,Fwoman, before joining West Yorkshire
OL,15,FPolice. One of the offences took place
OL,16,Fwhile he was a student officer.
OL,18,FBoth offences were reported to police
OL,19,Fafter he joined the force. He was
OL,20,Fsuspended at the start of the
OL,21,Finvestigation.
