OL,3,CRapist police officer jailed
OL,5,FBottomley was jailed for four years
OL,6,Fand will be on the Sex Offenders
OL,7,FRegister for life.
OL,9,FA formal misconduct hearing will take
OL,10,Fplace in July with a view to banning
OL,11,Fhim from policing.
OL,13,FFollowing Bottomley's conviction in
OL,14,FApril, Det Ch Supt Tanya Wilkins said:
OL,15,F"The victim has shown immense courage
OL,16,Fin coming forward to report these
OL,17,Foffences.
